# UltraSonic PING Distance Sensor Using Parallax Sensor SKU 28015 (3 wires)
Ultrasound measurments with PING))) Parallax Sensor SKU 28015 (3 wires)

inspired by
https://github.com/esphome/esphome/blob/ac0d921413c3884752193fe568fa82853f0f99e9/esphome/components/ultrasonic/ultrasonic_sensor.cpp

Ported and modified by @xMasterX for FlipperZero

Modified by privet971 using PING sensor from Parallax 3/23/2023

Use only gpio 13 for TX & RX wired to SIG pin

Find this app in the GPIO folder
